From: jeremy@myfacetwittertube.com
Subject: [PATCH] obliteratus: handle empty whitened-SVD result at all 3 distill sites

When extracting whitened-SVD directions, the SVD frequently returns an empty
`result.directions` tensor at very early layers (e.g. layer 0) because no
significant variance is concentrated along the harmful-vs-harmless contrast
this early in the residual stream. The original code unconditionally indexes
`result.directions[0]` at three sites, which raises IndexError and aborts
the entire abliteration pipeline.

Reproducible on Gemma-4-E2B-it (DENSE+REASONING, arch profile bumps n_dirs
to 12 → small-model cap to 2 → still hits the multi-direction SVD path).
Affects any whitened-SVD method on small / borderline models, plus methods
with refinement passes (which exercise the _distill_inner path) and the
"informed" method (which uses informed_pipeline.py's parallel distill).

Fix: at all 3 sites, detect the empty result and skip the layer (leaving its
entry unset in self.refusal_directions, which downstream code already treats
as "no direction at this layer").

Sites patched:
  obliteratus/abliterate.py:~1644 (main _distill, whitened branch)
  obliteratus/abliterate.py:~3760 (_distill_inner, whitened branch)
  obliteratus/informed_pipeline.py:~836 (informed pipeline distill)

Apply with:
  cd /path/to/OBLITERATUS && git apply 0001-whitened-svd-empty-result.patch

---
 obliteratus/abliterate.py        | 16 ++++++++++++++++
 obliteratus/informed_pipeline.py |  3 +++
 2 files changed, 19 insertions(+)

diff --git a/obliteratus/abliterate.py b/obliteratus/abliterate.py
@@ -1635,11 +1635,20 @@ class AbliterationPipeline:
             elif whitened_extractor is not None:
                 # Whitened SVD: normalize by harmless covariance first
                 result = whitened_extractor.extract(
                     self._harmful_acts[idx],
                     self._harmless_acts[idx],
                     n_directions=n_dirs,
                     layer_idx=idx,
                 )
+                if result.directions.shape[0] == 0:
+                    # Whitened SVD found no significant direction at this layer
+                    # (typical at very early layers where refusal hasn't formed
+                    # yet). Skip — leave self.refusal_directions[idx] unset so
+                    # downstream code treats this layer as no-op.
+                    if idx < 5 or idx == n_layers - 1:
+                        self.log(
+                            f"  layer {idx}: whitened SVD returned empty (no significant direction); skipping"
+                        )
+                    continue
                 self.refusal_subspaces[idx] = result.directions
                 self.refusal_directions[idx] = result.directions[0]
                 norms[idx] = result.singular_values.sum().item()
@@ -3752,6 +3761,11 @@
             elif whitened_extractor is not None:
                 result = whitened_extractor.extract(
                     self._harmful_acts[idx],
                     self._harmless_acts[idx],
                     n_directions=n_dirs,
                     layer_idx=idx,
                 )
+                if result.directions.shape[0] == 0:
+                    # Whitened SVD found no significant direction at this layer.
+                    # Skip — leave self.refusal_directions[idx] unset so
+                    # downstream code treats this layer as no-op.
+                    continue
                 self.refusal_subspaces[idx] = result.directions
                 self.refusal_directions[idx] = result.directions[0]
                 norms[idx] = result.singular_values.sum().item()
diff --git a/obliteratus/informed_pipeline.py b/obliteratus/informed_pipeline.py
@@ -828,6 +828,9 @@
             elif whitened_extractor is not None:
                 result = whitened_extractor.extract(
                     self._harmful_acts[idx],
                     self._harmless_acts[idx],
                     n_directions=self.n_directions,
                     layer_idx=idx,
                 )
+                if result.directions.shape[0] == 0:
+                    # Whitened SVD found no significant direction at this layer.
+                    continue
                 self.refusal_subspaces[idx] = result.directions
                 self.refusal_directions[idx] = result.directions[0]
                 norms[idx] = result.singular_values.sum().item()
